    ],
    "if_you_wanna_use_it": "Pick a building metaphor — house, cathedral, staircase, hallway — and map each section of your song to a part of that structure.",
    "examples_for_if_you_wanna_use_it": [
      "Treat your intro as the front door, verse as hallway, chorus as bright central room, and bridge as a hidden back staircase, like the floor-by-floor expansion in “Ain’t No Mountain High Enough.”",
